  "prompt": "Can I use my debit card as credit card on Airbnb?",
  "response": "Yes, you can typically use a debit card as a credit card on Airbnb. When making a reservation, just select your debit card as the payment method. Keep in mind that your debit card may need to have a Visa, MasterCard, Discover, or American Express logo on it for it to be accepted. Additionally, ensure that your debit card has sufficient funds and that your bank allows transactions to be processed like credit. Always check Airbnb's latest payment policies and your bank's regulations for the most accurate information.",
